name: CIS Automotive
title: CIS Automotive
description: Uncover the secrets of your automotive market. We provide detailed realtime automotive market data across the US for major car brands and models. Our VinDecode endpoint is now available.

endpoints.name: listingsByRegion
endpoints.description: Returns a dealer's listings over up to the last 45 days by dealer ID. The ID can be found by calling the /getDealers endpoint. Listing keys are: vin, askPrice, msrp, isNew, firstSeen, lastSeen, modelName, brandName. Results are paginated in chunks of up to 20 vehicles. Prices are in the dealer's local currency (generally USD).

endpoints.name: listings
endpoints.description: Returns a dealer's listings over the last 45 days. Listing keys are: vin, askPrice, msrp, isNew, firstSeen, lastSeen, modelName, brandName. Results are paginated in chunks of up to 20 vehicles. Prices are in the dealer's local currency (generally USD).

endpoints.name: getDealersByRegion
endpoints.description: Premium. Dealership information in a given region. Returns name, address, state, zipCode, and IDs. Results are paginated with up to 30 results per page.
